Initialized(uint8).details: Triggered when the contract has been initialized or reinitialized.

params.armyAddress: The address of the army which received units

calculateTokensForExactUnits(uint256).details: Returns valid output only for integer unitsToBuy value (in 1e0 precision)

returns._0: Amount of tokens needed for unitsToBuy

era().details: Value is dereferenced from proxy storage and world

params.initParams: Encoded init params (every world asset has own knowledge how to extract data from it)

swapTokensForExactUnits(address,address,.details: If tokensOwner == address(0) -> tokens will be taken from msg.senderIf tokensOwner != address(0) and tokensOwner has given allowance to msg.sender >= amount of tokens for units -> tokens will be taken from tokensOwner

params.maxTokensToSell: Maximum amount of tokens to be taken for exact amount of units
params.settlementAddress: Settlement address, army of which, will receive units

returns._0: Amount of units bought by tokens

swapTokensForExactUnitsByRegion(address,.details: Even though function is opened it can be called only by regionIf tokensOwner == address(0) -> tokens will be taken from msg.senderIf tokensOwner != address(0) and tokensOwner has given allowance to msg.sender >= amount of tokens for units -> tokens will be taken from tokensOwner

params.maxTokensToSell: Maximum amount of tokens to be taken for exact amount of units
params.settlementAddress: Settlement address, army of which, will receive units

returns._0: Amount of units bought by tokens

world().details: Value is dereferenced from proxy storage

lastPurchaseTime.details: Updated every time when #swapTokensForExactUnits or #swapTokensForExactUnitsByRegion is called

relatedRegion.details: Immutable, initialized on the region creation

unitPrice.details: Updated every time when #swapTokensForExactUnits or #swapTokensForExactUnitsByRegion is called

unitTypeId.details: Immutable, initialized on the region creation

CannotHireUnitsDueToTheirCostIsHigherTha.notice: Thrown when attempting to hire units due to their cost is being higher than max tokens to sell specified

CannotHireUnitsExceedingArmyUnitsLimit().notice: Thrown when attempting to hire more units than army limit allows

CannotHireUnitsExceedingTransactionLimit.notice: Thrown when attempting to hire more units than transaction limit

CannotHireUnitsForArmyWhichSettlementDoe.notice: Thrown when attempting to hire units in wrong units pool

CannotHireUnitsInvalidUnitsToBuySpecifie.notice: Thrown when attempting to hire units with invalid units to buy specified

CannotHireUnitsWhileArmyIsManeuvering().notice: Thrown when attempting to hire units while army is maneuvering

CannotHireUnitsWhileArmyIsNotOnHomePosit.notice: Thrown when attempting to hire units while army is not on home position

CannotHireUnitsWhileArmyIsStunned().notice: Thrown when attempting to hire units while army is stunned

OnlyActiveGame().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called in active game (started and not finished)

OnlyMightyCreator().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called by mighty creator

OnlyRelatedRegion().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called by related region

OnlyRulerOrWorldAsset().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called by ruler or world asset

OnlyWorldAssetFromSameEra().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called by world asset from same era

UnknownInputParameter().notice: Thrown when attempting to call function by providing unknown parameter
